data.description: JUST REDUCED $20,000 - GREAT VALUE & LOCATION! Charming Northridge single story home on a great street! Cute curb appeal. This fantastic 3 bedroom/2 bath property is set on an oversized lot with a huge back yard! Nicely remodeled throughout and move in ready. 1254 square feet of living space on a grand 7600 square foot lot. Open concept living/dining and kitchen areas that flow to a HUGE covered patio and a giant back yard. Plenty of room for a pool or to expand! Remodeled kitchen with custom shaker cabinets, granite countertops. Living room/great room with fireplace. Three bedrooms total, with a primary bedroom suite that is located in its own wing and is highlighted by an ensuite remodeled full bath. Two additional generously sized bedrooms are adjacent to another redone full bath. New electrical panel. Newer roof and updated HVAC. Recessed lighting and dual pane windows. Hardwood floors throughout most of the house. New flooring at the formal entry and kitchen areas, new carpet in one of the bedrooms. Large, direct access, oversized two car garage (incredible ADU potential) – and an extended driveway for multiple vehicles. Solar panels are installed, ($142 a month) providing incredible LADWP electrical savings year round. Centrally located to the Northridge mall, award winning schools, shopping, restaurants and the best of the valley. Don’t miss your chance!
